message.content:
Day 1:
Breakfast: Overnight oats with chia seeds, berries, and maple syrup.
Lunch: Quinoa salad with roasted vegetables, avocado, and lemon vinaigrette.
Dinner: Grilled tofu with steamed broccoli and brown rice.

Day 2:
Breakfast: Green smoothie with spinach, banana, almond milk, and flaxseeds.
Lunch: Lemon-tahini dressing over roasted sweet potato salad with cucumber and tomatoes.
Dinner: Baked salmon with asparagus and brown rice pilaf.

Day 3:
Breakfast: Vegan chia pudding with fresh fruit.
Lunch: Zucchini noodles with cashew cream sauce and avocado.
Dinner: Lentil soup with a side of whole grain bread.

Day 4:
Breakfast: Chocolate avocado toast with a banana.
Lunch: Quinoa bowl with roasted cauliflower, cranberries, and tahini dressing.
Dinner: Vegetable stir-fry with tofu and brown rice.

Day 5:
Breakfast: Smoothie bowl with frozen berries, mango, and acai powder.
Lunch: Hummus and veggie wrap with cucumber, tomato, and lettuce.
Dinner: Vegan mushroom stroganoff over brown rice.

Day 6:
Breakfast: Apple cinnamon oatmeal with almond milk.
Lunch: Roasted beet salad with goat cheese and walnut vinaigrette.
Dinner: Grilled vegetable kebabs with quinoa and a side of guacamole.

Day 7:
Breakfast: Vegan chocolate protein shake with almond milk, banana, and peanut butter.
Lunch: Chickpea salad sandwich with spinach, tomato, and avocado.
Dinner: Vegan shepherd's pie with roasted vegetables and mashed sweet potatoes.
